languages.text: "У нас мало клиентов, желающих — и способных — приобретать груды пластали и священных механизмов размером с небольшой астероид. Поэтому каталог, который редко пополняется, все равно остается актуальным".

traits.locale_text: "У нас мало клиентов, желающих — и способных — приобретать груды пластали и священных механизмов размером с небольшой астероид. Поэтому каталог, который редко пополняется, все равно остается актуальным".

languages.text: "We don't have many customers who are willing — and able — to acquire enormous piles of plasteel and sacred tech the size of a small asteroid. So our catalogue rarely acquires new stock but remains up to date."

languages.text: 「膨大な量のプラスチールと、小惑星ほどの大きさの神聖な技術を確保しようとする…そして実際に入手できる顧客は多くありません。ですから、私たちの目録は新規在庫が記載されることは滅多にありませんが、最新情報が保たれています」

languages.text: “我们的客户大多既无意愿、也无能力购买大量塑钢或像小行星大小的神圣科技，因此我们的目录很少上新。不过，总体还是比较齐全的。”
languages.original_text: "We don't have many customers who are willing — and able — to acquire enormous piles of plasteel and sacred tech the size of a small asteroid. So our catalogue rarely acquires new stock but remains up to date."

languages.text: « Nous n'avons pas beaucoup de clients désirant – ou pouvant – acquérir de grandes quantités de plastacier ou de la technologie sacrée de la taille d'un petit astéroïde. Notre catalogue ne s'enrichit donc que rarement de nouveaux articles, mais il reste à jour. »
languages.original_text: "We don't have many customers who are willing — and able — to acquire enormous piles of plasteel and sacred tech the size of a small asteroid. So our catalogue rarely acquires new stock but remains up to date."

traits.locale_text: « Nous n'avons pas beaucoup de clients désirant – ou pouvant – acquérir de grandes quantités de plastacier ou de la technologie sacrée de la taille d'un petit astéroïde. Notre catalogue ne s'enrichit donc que rarement de nouveaux articles, mais il reste à jour. »

languages.text: «No tenemos muchos clientes que quieran, ni puedan, adquirir cantidades ingentes de plastiacero y tecnología sagrada del tamaño de un asteroide pequeño. Por eso rara vez encargamos existencias nuevas, pero nuestro catálogo no está desfasado».
languages.original_text: "We don't have many customers who are willing — and able — to acquire enormous piles of plasteel and sacred tech the size of a small asteroid. So our catalogue rarely acquires new stock but remains up to date."

languages.text: "Wir haben nicht viele Kunden, die bereit ... und in der Lage ... sind, riesigen Mengen von Plaststahl und heiliger Tech von der Größe eines kleinen Asteroiden zu erwerben. Unser Katalog ist also auch ohne neue Ware stets aktuell."
languages.original_text: "We don't have many customers who are willing — and able — to acquire enormous piles of plasteel and sacred tech the size of a small asteroid. So our catalogue rarely acquires new stock but remains up to date."

languages.text: "Muazzam miktarda plasçelik ve küçük bir asteroit kadar çok kutsal teknoloji sağlamaya istekli olup bunları sağlayabilecek pek müşterimiz yok. Dolayısıyla kataloğumuza nadiren yeni şeyler eklenir, yine de güncel tutarız."
languages.original_text: "We don't have many customers who are willing — and able — to acquire enormous piles of plasteel and sacred tech the size of a small asteroid. So our catalogue rarely acquires new stock but remains up to date."

traits.locale_text: "Muazzam miktarda plastiçelik ve küçük bir asteroit boyutundaki kutsal teknolojiler sağlamaya istekli ve de bunları sağlamayı başarabilecek pek fazla müşterimiz yok. Dolayısıyla kataloğumuza yeni şeyler dâhil olduğu nadirdir ama yine de günceldir."
